dc_title_s: Syria : route of the American Archaeological Expedition of 1899-1900
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Also shows Bedouin encampments, tombs of saints, minarets, ruins, and towers. "Based upon map by Dr. Richard Kiepert, published with Baron von Oppenheim's 'Vom Mittelmeere zum Persischen Golf' in 1899."
dc_subject_sm: Oppenheim, Max, Freiherr von, 1860-1946—Vom Mittelmeer zum Persischen Golf durch den Haurän, die Syrische Wüste und Mesopotamien
